(Step-By-Step Method) Tj
T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Machine Learning.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind training data, patterns,) Tj
T*
(prediction, and models.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct logical procedure step by step instead of jumping to the answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
